  <summary date="2020-02-27T19:26:46Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Stop the Attack on Local Taxpayers Act or the SALT Act

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to (1) repeal the $10,000 limitation on individual income tax deductions for certain state and local taxes, and (2) increase the top individual income tax rate to 39.6% (currently 37%).</summary>
